clause_text: = Incentive FSI at location ‘A’ in CDS X ASR value of Land at location ‘A’/ASR value of Land at location ‘B’ Where, location ‘A’ refers to the location where incentive FSI in CDS is generated. Location ‘B’ is the new location where such incentive FSI is to be utilized.
